data.title: Top Academic Performers
data.meta_description: Broward College recognizes students have demonstrated a high level of achievement and success in earning good grades and maintaining high grade point averages (GPAs).​​
data.text:
Summer 2024 Academic All-Stars

Broward College is pleased to showcase its academic all-stars and we wish you continued success in your pursuit of your degree. These students have demonstrated a high level of achievement and success in earning good grades and maintaining high grade point averages (GPAs).

Attention!

This site is best viewed in a modern browser and is not compatible with Internet Explorer (IE). Please use another browser, such Chrome, Safari, Edge, or Firefox for the best user experience.
